# Profit Or Loss Insurance Result Amount

## identifier
de8497

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, for the duration of the relevant period, of the insurance result. 

This item represents the sum of the underwriting result and any investment income on assets backing insurance liabilities net of investment expenses on assets backing insurance liabilities.

Underwriting result represents net premium revenue, in accordance with the Prudential Standards, less net claims expense and total underwriting expenses as determined by the relevant Accounting Standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=ProfitOrLoss.Insurance.Result.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr3.02.05
- period=duration
